snippet.title: Trover Saves the Universe | Extended Commercial Spot | PS4 Out Now
snippet.description:
https://troversavestheuniverse.com/buy

From the co-creator of Rick and Morty comes Trover Saves the Universe. Your pups are missing. The cosmos is at stake. Only you and Trover can save everything in this bizarre comedy adventure created by Justin Roiland.

Out now on PlayStation 4 and PlayStation VR, and June 4 on PC via Steam, Oculus Store and Epic Game Store!
